 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721a9cb60e67aad7d7438acf4d329fdeed90b9f9","tid":13244,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"做低階野唔夠其他支那牌子平<br />\n中高階唔夠歐美日韓鬥"},{"pid":"ea1e723d6be99b386f43624163b53a56a44be1e6","tid":13244,"uid":41289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"小米啊，免費派都吾用啦"},{"pid":"e3aec0566ccff5161f239dfc6d4392a86d163c74","tid":13244,"uid":36585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌米唔係出部無邊框設計咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果部野根本量產唔到<br />\n唔好以為整到咁好似好勁咁<br />\n其實各大電話品牌都整到出黎，只無好難量產化整黎哂氣</blockquote><br />\n點解量產唔到？</blockquote><br />\n個手機個殻好似得5%良率"},{"pid":"85652083621e1c68f94bb0b9c243269ce5872868","tid":13244,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb54a5d8175d9b62bdcc2a61265e2d966a202313","tid":13244,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌米唔係出部無邊框設計咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果部野根本量產唔到<br />\n唔好以為整到咁好似好勁咁<br />\n其實各大電話品牌都整到出黎，只無好難量產化整黎哂氣</blockquote><br />\n點解量產唔到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做過生產都知一件貨同埋量產係差好遠<br />\n一件貨可以用好多資源整出黎<br />\n甚至好多位用人手整<br />\n<br />\n量產要上生產線<br />\n冇機配合到 = 晒鳩氣"},{"pid":"1193c2706bec967ea7d62a86f293b461c14c669a","tid":13244,"uid":17314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":